--- !u!114 &885823535
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 885823534}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 02dc830dd6e0a194bbfe391c99606bdc, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  item:
    itemName: Pain Killer
    requestTags:
    - Comfort
    - Escape
    consequenceLines:
    - "\"The ache doesn\u2019t go away this time. It spreads instead, slow and heavy,
      like something settling deeper inside me. I feel it even when I try not to.
      I feel worse.\""
    - "\"My head feels clearer for a second, then worse. It\u2019s like something
      that used to protect me is gone. I don\u2019t think I can ignore it anymore.
      I feel worse.\" "
    statTag: Self
    value: 14
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - These are supposed to make things stop hurting. I hold the bottle tight.
    - The pills rattle when I shake them. Mom says they help me.
    - "I wonder if they\u2019d help me feel normal again. Or at least quiet."
