--- !u!114 &1160658176
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1160658174}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 02dc830dd6e0a194bbfe391c99606bdc, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  item:
    itemName: Fuel Can
    requestTags:
    - Warmth
    - Protection
    consequenceLines:
    - "\"The house feels colder tonight. Not just the air\u2026everything feels slower,
      like it\u2019s losing energy. It\u2019s harder to stay warm. The house feels
      weaker.\""
    - "\"Something vital is missing. The house doesn\u2019t feel alive anymore, just
      empty and still. I don\u2019t think it can keep us safe like this. The house
      feels weaker.\""
    statTag: Home
    value: 14
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - It smells strong, like it could keep the house warm if we needed it.
    - "I don\u2019t like how dangerous it feels, but I know it could protect the
      house from the cold."
    - It sits there waiting, like something meant to keep the house going no matter
      what.
