  item:
    itemName: Egg
    requestTags:
    - Hunger
    - Comfort
    consequenceLines:
    - " \u201CMy stomach twists a little when I think about it. That was something
      I actually needed. I think I gave up more than I should have. I feel worse.\u201D"
    statTag: Self
    value: 14
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - "I eat it even when I\u2019m not that hungry. It makes the feeling go away
      for a little while. "
    - "It doesn\u2019t always taste right anymore, but I still need it."
