--- !u!114 &1393250222
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1393250220}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 02dc830dd6e0a194bbfe391c99606bdc, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  item:
    itemName: Chair
    requestTags:
    - Comfort
    - Memory
    consequenceLines:
    - "\"The house feels emptier without it. There\u2019s nowhere to sit together
      anymore, nowhere to stay close. It feels like something small but important
      is missing. The house feels weaker.\" "
    - "\"I notice Jane stands more now. Not because she wants to, but because there\u2019s
      nothing left to sit on. It feels like I took away something that made things
      easier in the house. The house feels weaker.\" "
    statTag: Home
    value: 14
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - The wood creaks when someone moves it across the floor. It has always been
      annoying.
    - "It\u2019s just a chair, but it feels like it belongs here more than anything
      else. Like the room would notice if it was gone.  "
