  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 02dc830dd6e0a194bbfe391c99606bdc, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  item:
    itemName: Curtain
    requestTags:
    - Protection
    - Silence
    consequenceLines:
    - "\"The window feels too open now. Like something outside can see in, even when
      I turn away. I don\u2019t like how exposed the room feels. The house feels
      weaker.\" "
    - "\"The light doesn\u2019t stay out anymore. It creeps in at night, thin and
      cold. It feels like we\u2019ve lost a layer of safety. The house feels weaker.\""
    statTag: Home
    value: 14
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - It blocks the window when it gets too dark outside. I think the house it closed.
    - The fabric is soft, but it keeps things out of the house. Or maybe keeps things
      in.
