  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 02dc830dd6e0a194bbfe391c99606bdc, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  item:
    itemName: Nest
    requestTags:
    - Protection
    - Memory
    - Hunger
    consequenceLines:
    - "\"I keep thinking about what could have been there. A family meant to grow,
      but didn\u2019t. It feels like I took that away. We feel farther apart.\" "
    statTag: Family
    value: 14
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - A nest. The eggs are small and warm. A family is supposed to grow here.
    - I think this nest came from a bird we saw last summer. I hope their little
      family makes it through the winter.
