    consequenceLines:
    - "\u201CThe kitchen feels less secure now. I keep noticing empty spaces where
      things should be. If something happened, I don\u2019t think I\u2019d be ready.
      I feel worse.\u201D"
    - "\u201CI didn\u2019t realize how important it was until it was gone. I feel
      a little more exposed now. Like I lost something that was supposed to protect
      us. I feel worse.\u201D"
    statTag: Self
    value: 14
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - I use it to cut food, but I try not to think about what else it could do.
    - "I don\u2019t like holding it, but I feel better knowing it\u2019s here."
    - "I look at it longer than I should. I don\u2019t know why. "
