--- !u!114 &2120959671
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 2120959670}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 02dc830dd6e0a194bbfe391c99606bdc, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  item:
    itemName: Letter
    requestTags:
    - Information
    - Memory
    - Comfort
    consequenceLines:
    - " \u201CJane keeps reaching for it, then stopping like she forgot where it
      went. Her face looks different, like something important slipped away. I think
      I took more than just paper. We feel farther apart.\u201D"
    - " \u201CJane sits there quieter than before, like she\u2019s trying to remember
      something she can\u2019t quite hold onto. The room feels emptier, not just
      physically. I don\u2019t think she feels the same without it. We feel farther
      apart.\u201D"
    statTag: Family
    value: 14
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - My sister reads it everyday even though I think she already knows what it says.
    - "It must tell my sister something important\u2026 she never puts it away."
    - "I think my sister is scared she\u2019ll forget if she doesn\u2019t keep looking
      at it."
